description.en:
Change is a rapidly growing FinTech providing everyone in Europe access to exciting investments. Thousands of people from 31 EU countries trust Change to build their financial future and have traded over 85+ million euros.

CAG token will be used to purchase services through Change. Currently, users can order a debit card using CAG through our customer support team.

ico_data.short_desc: Change is the first global decentralised crypto bank
ico_data.description: In addition to a crypto payment card, Change allows you to invest your cryptos between a variety of Financial Technology companies within its marketplace. The first-of-a-kind decentralised bank, where each service is provided by a specialised company.
